\imt1 Asulumaęž‰noęž‰ towoęž‰ we
\ip Tesalonaika saęž‰s kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰noęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰loęž‰ miaęž‰nigab aęž‰noęž‰ dinafa moęž‰fanda asuloęž‰. Kalu nolbaęž‰ saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰ koęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰labiki, Foloęž‰ Sales, Timoti iliyoęž‰ Tesalonaika kalukaęž‰isale ililoęž‰ hala asulab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ digale fanda asulumaęž‰ki saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰.
\ip Foęž‰l e saęž‰lakiyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suloęž‰ miaęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ semoęž‰faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰kaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ hoęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰ semoęž‰faęž‰laęž‰dowab amioęž‰, eleloęž‰ gola baęž‰baęž‰noęž‰ kalu nowoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dotaęž‰gaęž‰, Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰ gis diaęž‰ib.
\ip Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰ saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, tilidabuwoęž‰ halale kagayaki, hidaęž‰yoęž‰ yab aęž‰noęž‰ dimaęž‰ki sioęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ininaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ dinafa tilidomaęž‰ki, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ nanog diaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰boęž‰sulumaęž‰ki, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalu nol asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰kiyoęž‰, moęž‰foęž‰s we aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰.
\c 1
\s1 Ili tilidabuwoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dowaki, mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰
\p 
\v 1 Foęž‰l ne, Salesoęž‰, Timotiyoęž‰ niliyoęž‰ to we saęž‰saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, Do Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ Alan Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale Tesalonaika saęž‰s usamiloęž‰ sab oęž‰moęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰toęž‰l.
\v 2 \x - \xo 1.2 \xt Lom 1.7\x*Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ Alan Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man oęž‰liaęž‰ haęž‰sa mesaęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰ dofoęž‰meleaęž‰ki, Godemoęž‰ dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l.
\p 
\v 3 Ni nao i, gili tilidabuwoęž‰ anayaki halaidoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰ndab aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gegeleboęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ gi usamioęž‰ alan dowaęž‰i haęž‰nab koęž‰loęž‰ niliyoęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo Godemoęž‰ mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰melaęž‰niki. Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ dimidaęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ mada nafayoęž‰ oęž‰m.
\v 4 \x - \xo 1.4 \xt 2Kol 7.4, 1Tes 2.19\x*Hidaęž‰yoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ nagaloęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ giloęž‰wa faęž‰laęž‰dowaęž‰lab amioęž‰, gioęž‰ halale kagayaki, tilidabuwoęž‰ oęž‰taęž‰li sen koęž‰loęž‰ nioęž‰ saęž‰s nola haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidaęž‰lab aęž‰laęž‰liki, gili wiyoęž‰ wabulu saęž‰laęž‰lab.
\p 
\v 5 Giliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale digaloęž‰le alobaęž‰daęž‰sen aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ fanda widaęž‰lab. Gioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ enedoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lab usa silikiyoęž‰, hidaęž‰yoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰woęž‰ diaęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ aęž‰na mesaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰li koęž‰loęž‰lab aęž‰laęž‰liki widoęž‰.
\v 6 \x - \xo 1.6 \xt Lom 12.19\x*Gode eyoęž‰ digaloęž‰le moęž‰walilaęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰, kalu abeyoęž‰ gimoęž‰loęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰ dimiaęž‰lab oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ kalu aęž‰noęž‰ waęž‰deaki hidaęž‰yoęž‰woęž‰ dimiaęž‰ib.
\v 7 \x - \xo 1.7 \xt 1Tes 3.13\x*Hidaęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰lab gi aęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ nioęž‰loęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ haęž‰saloęž‰ mesaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ dimiaęž‰ib. Yaęž‰su Alan e Hebene aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ handalowakiyoęž‰, ene maęž‰mulaęž‰ kalu halaidoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ de waęž‰sowa oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ yab aęž‰namioęž‰ haęž‰saloęž‰ mesaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na dimiaęž‰ib.
\v 8 \x - \xo 1.8 \xt Ais 66.15\x*Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Godeloęž‰ moęž‰asulaęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰ Yaęž‰su Alanaęž‰ to nafaloęž‰ moęž‰kudu ane aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰, Eyoęž‰ aęž‰na waęž‰deaki falasilaęž‰maęž‰ib.
\v 9 \x - \xo 1.9 \xt Ais 2.10\x*Imoęž‰loęž‰ falasilaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ we. Iyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Alan oęž‰liaęž‰ ene halaidoęž‰ alan aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ anib amioęž‰ moęž‰meseaęž‰ki, koęž‰naęž‰le taęž‰faęž‰ib. Gode eyoęž‰ iyoęž‰ mogagilaki, falasiloęž‰ aęž‰naka dofoęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰meleaęž‰ki taęž‰faęž‰ib.
\v 10 \x - \xo 1.10 \xt Kolo 3.4\x*Yaęž‰su Alan eloęž‰ yab hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰, tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale enedoęž‰ daęž‰feyoęž‰ i aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Alanoęž‰ wabudakiyoęž‰, molo asulumaęž‰ib. Nililoęž‰ gimoęž‰loęž‰ widoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ giliyoęž‰ tilidabu koęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰loęž‰ i oęž‰liaęž‰ ua gasamaęž‰ib.\fig Yaęž‰suwoęž‰ yakiyoęž‰, hidaęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰lab gimoęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰saloęž‰ mesaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ dimiaęž‰ib.|alt="Receiving reward" src="18_Jb_01_04_RG_gr.tif" size="col" copy="Â© Sweet Publishing http://sweetpublishing.com, licensed under a CC: BY-SA 3.0 Unported licence." ref="1.7"\fig*
\p 
\v 11-12 \x - \xo 1.11-12 \xt Kolo 1.9, 1Tes 1.2-3\x*Nili Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso Alan oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nioęž‰ kanulu alifaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, Yaęž‰suwaęž‰loęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ giloęž‰ amiloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ ene wiyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ wabudabikiyoęž‰, Yaęž‰su eyoęž‰ gili wiyoęž‰loęž‰ wabulumaęž‰kiyoęž‰, niliyoęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo gioęž‰ Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰sen. Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ gimoęž‰loęž‰ man nafa dimidamaęž‰kiloęž‰ hoęž‰idoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ ililimaęž‰ki, dulugu saęž‰laęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ man nafa gililoęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ asulan aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰, Godeya tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ ilikiloęž‰ nanog dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene halaidoęž‰waęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰ki, dulugu saęž‰laęž‰sen.
\c 2
\s1 Gode oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ gisdoęž‰ dowaęž‰senoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib
\p 
\v 1 Ni nao i, Alan Yaęž‰su Kelisowoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ miaęž‰nigab aęž‰namioęž‰, nioęž‰ e oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ gasayakiloęž‰ kegenemaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, niyoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l.
\v 2 Kalu Alanaęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ oęž‰ma faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰ koęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰likiyoęž‰, kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ widaęž‰labaęž‰le, moęž‰dinali saęž‰laęž‰labele, moęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰soęž‰ nili iligaęž‰foęž‰kaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰likiloęž‰ agelab aęž‰noęž‰, gioęž‰ dabulalega, iligakiyoęž‰ kele asulaęž‰soęž‰bo.
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 2.3 \xt 1Tim 4.1, 1Yoęž‰n 2.18, 4.3\x*Kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dinali saęž‰lalikiyoęž‰ gioęž‰ tilidaęž‰daęž‰soęž‰bo. Moęž‰woęž‰ Alanaęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ oęž‰semoęž‰faęž‰laęž‰dowab amioęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰loęž‰ Gode oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰iyakiloęž‰ gola baęž‰baęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib. Hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰ ele saefaęž‰loęž‰ gola baęž‰baęž‰noęž‰ kalu imilig aęž‰noęž‰ kalaba faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib. Kalu aęž‰noęž‰ deyaęž‰ mogagilaęž‰maęž‰ki daęž‰fe alifoęž‰lab.
\v 4 \x - \xo 2.4 \xt Ese 28.2, Dan 11.36\x*Kalu aęž‰noęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowalikiyoęž‰, eyoęž‰ Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ madali gode kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰loęž‰ wabulu saęž‰laęž‰lab oęž‰liaęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ gis dimidaki, enenaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ kailaki, nol aęž‰noęž‰ waęž‰laęž‰ saęž‰maęž‰ib. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ eyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ maliloęž‰ a usa haęž‰naęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ silikiyoęž‰, â€śGodeleyoęž‰ nekaęž‰â€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰melaęž‰ib.
\p 
\v 5 Ne gi oęž‰liaęž‰ silikiyoęž‰, to aęž‰noęž‰ widoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰ gaęž‰lilaęž‰yaęž‰le?
\v 6 Ele saefaęž‰loęž‰ gola baęž‰baęž‰noęž‰ kalu aęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰lende imilaba kalaba faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰kiyoęž‰, oęž‰goęž‰ e kafoęž‰lab, aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ gioęž‰ asulab.
\v 7-8 \x - \xo 2.7-8 \xt Ais 11.4, Kala 19.15\x*Henfeloęž‰ wenamioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰iyan man aęž‰noęž‰ nanogoęž‰ woęž‰noęž‰leboęž‰ diaęž‰lab koęž‰sega, noloęž‰ e kaęž‰laęž‰lab. Tif amioęž‰ kafoęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ dilaęž‰maęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰, ele saefaęž‰loęž‰ gola baęž‰baęž‰noęž‰ kalu aęž‰noęž‰ kalab amioęž‰ aęž‰na faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib. E faęž‰laęž‰dotaęž‰gaęž‰ aęž‰lalikiyoęž‰, Alan Yaęž‰suwoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ yaęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, ene mehoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ ene hoęž‰len halaidoęž‰ soęž‰soęž‰idab oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ kalu aęž‰noęž‰ sanalaęž‰maęž‰ib.
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 2.9 \xt Kala 13.11-13\x*Kalu aęž‰noęž‰, Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰yaęž‰ ene halaidoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰ halaidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ widakiyoęž‰, eyoęž‰ madali dikidaki, ele baęž‰baęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ molo haęž‰naęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ dimidamaęž‰ib.
\v 10 Kalukaęž‰isale mogagilaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ dobaęž‰daęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ dikidaki, kalu aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ man mogagoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ dimidamaęž‰ib. Kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰noęž‰ to hendeleyoęž‰ asulumaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ gola baęž‰dabiki, Gode eyoęž‰ iyoęž‰ moęž‰gasiliab koęž‰loęž‰ iyoęž‰ mogagilaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ dobaęž‰daęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰lab.
\v 11 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰noęž‰ madali to saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ hendele aęž‰noęž‰koęž‰ tilidabumaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ iyoęž‰ aęž‰naka taęž‰faęž‰ib.
\v 12 Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ iyoęž‰ to hendele aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰tilidaęž‰daki, man mogagoęž‰le aęž‰noęž‰ sagalaęž‰li dimidaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰laliki, Gode eyoęž‰ iyoęž‰ moęž‰walilaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ falasilaęž‰maęž‰ib.
\s1 Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ dimaęž‰ki daęž‰feyoęž‰
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 2.13 \xt Aęž‰fe 1.4, 2Tes 1.3\x*Koęž‰sega nao i, Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ mada alan asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ niliyoęž‰ gi aęž‰noęž‰ asulakiyoęž‰, Godemoęž‰woęž‰ mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰melaęž‰niki. Moęž‰woęž‰ gioęž‰ to hendele aęž‰noęž‰ tilidaęž‰dabiki, Godeyaęž‰ Mamayaęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ maliloęž‰ meleaęž‰ki taęž‰takiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ aęž‰na aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ gasili koęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laki, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ taminde amioęž‰ gi koęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰feyoęž‰.
\v 14 Aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰kiyoęž‰, nioęž‰ to nafayoęž‰ gimoęž‰ widaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ aęž‰na hoęž‰idoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ Alan Yaęž‰su Keliso E wabudab oęž‰leaumboęž‰, gili wiyoęž‰loęž‰ wabulu samaęž‰ki, Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ aęž‰na hoęž‰leli.
\v 15 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ ni nao i, nililoęž‰ towaęž‰loęž‰ widoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, moęž‰foęž‰s tamin amiloęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, giliyoęž‰ mada dinafa tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, halale taęž‰li dofoęž‰lubi.
\p 
\v 16 Nili Alan Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰ Do Gode oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nioęž‰ alan asulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, ene kanuloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nioęž‰ haęž‰sa dofoęž‰meleaęž‰ki taęž‰takiyoęž‰, tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ halale alitaki, sagalaęž‰li yasilimaęž‰ki taęž‰foęž‰.
\v 17 Eyoęž‰ gili asuloęž‰woęž‰ halale alitakiyoęž‰, to nafa gililoęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰lab oęž‰liaęž‰ man nafa dimidaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ egoęž‰le mada domaęž‰ki, niyoęž‰ gioęž‰ emoęž‰woęž‰ dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l.
\c 3
\s1 Gode eyoęž‰ asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰ki, dulugu saęž‰laęž‰bi
\p 
\v 1 To nowoęž‰ edaki saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l. Nao i giliyoęž‰ nioęž‰ asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰ki, Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰lubi. Alanaęž‰ to nafa aęž‰noęž‰ hen we tambo amioęž‰ boęž‰boęž‰ge daęž‰daęž‰i haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, giloęž‰ sagalaęž‰likiloęž‰ dabu oęž‰leau dabumaęž‰ki, Godemoęž‰woęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰lubi.
\v 2 Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalu noloęž‰ Alan amioęž‰ moęž‰tilidabu koęž‰loęž‰ mogagoęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab kaluwaęž‰ dagi amiloęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ nioęž‰ gaęž‰li meseaęž‰ki, giliyoęž‰ Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰lubi.
\p 
\v 3 Koęž‰sega Alan e gioęž‰ mada moęž‰gaęž‰lilaęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰, gimoęž‰woęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dimiaki, man mogagoęž‰leloęž‰ dimidaęž‰sen Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ mogagilabenaęž‰ki dinafa tilidomaęž‰ib.
\v 4 \x - \xo 3.4 \xt 2Kol 7.16, Gala 5.10\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰ Alana tilidaęž‰daki, nililoęž‰ gimoęž‰loęž‰ sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ giliyoęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, tifamioęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰koęž‰ dimidaęž‰li haęž‰naęž‰melaęž‰ib aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ nioęž‰ hendele tili asuloęž‰.
\v 5 Keliso eloęž‰ halale kagayab oęž‰leau giliyoęž‰loęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ diab amioęž‰ halale kagamaęž‰noęž‰ man oęž‰liaęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰, Alan eyoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ tili walamaęž‰ki, nioęž‰ Godemoęž‰ dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l.
\s1 Boęž‰sulakiyoęž‰ saęž‰soęž‰bo
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 3.6 \xt Lom 16.17\x*Nao i, nili Alan Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ wiya ilikiyoęž‰, niliyoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ we koęž‰loęž‰ gimoęž‰ salitoęž‰l. Kalu abeyoęž‰ to nililoęž‰ widabikiloęž‰ gililoęž‰ dabu aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰naki, ba madali boęž‰sulakiloęž‰ sab i oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ uayoęž‰ dowaęž‰soęž‰bo.
\v 7-8 \x - \xo 3.7-8 \xt Fili 3.17, 1Tes 2.9\x*To aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ fanda saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l. Nioęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰ silikiloęž‰ man dimidaęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰ gioęž‰ asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, giliyoęž‰loęž‰ man oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ ka kudu haęž‰naęž‰bi. Nioęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰ silikiyoęž‰ moęž‰boęž‰sulaki, maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ ba madaliyoęž‰ moęž‰diaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ naęž‰sen. Noęž‰noęž‰n moleyaęž‰ kililiaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ naęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, ni tili domaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ gioęž‰ kele asulabenaęž‰kiyoęž‰, niliyoęž‰ hoęž‰lenowoęž‰loęž‰ nuluwoęž‰loęž‰ nanogoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dimidaęž‰len.
\v 9 \x - \xo 3.9 \xt 1Kol 9.4, 1Tes 1.6\x*Nioęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ madali ka dimina aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰li koęž‰sega, aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰dimidaki, man nafa tifamiloęž‰ gililoęž‰ kudu haęž‰nakiloęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰, aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ widaki goęž‰.
\v 10 Hendele, nioęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰ silikiyoęž‰, ele we gimoęž‰woęž‰ widoęž‰. â€śKalu abeyoęž‰ nanogoęž‰ moęž‰dimidalega, e maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰maęž‰ib.â€ť
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 3.11 \xt 1Tim 5.13\x*Aęž‰laęž‰widoęž‰ koęž‰sega, oęž‰goęž‰ gi us amioęž‰ noloęž‰ boęž‰sulaki ba madali sakaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dabu. Iyoęž‰ inin nanogoęž‰ moęž‰diaki, kalu nolbaęž‰loęž‰ dimidab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laki nenelaęž‰sen.
\v 12 \x - \xo 3.12 \xt 1Tes 4.11\x*Nioęž‰ Alan Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ wi amioęž‰, to halaidoęž‰woęž‰ kalu i oęž‰ngoęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l. Gioęž‰ maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ maęž‰nikiyoęž‰, dinafa haęž‰sa siliki goęž‰noęž‰noęž‰ nanogoęž‰ dimidaęž‰lubi.
\v 13 \x - \xo 3.13 \xt Gala 6.9\x*Ni nao i, gioęž‰ man digaloęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰beakiyoęž‰ dowaęž‰soęž‰bo.
\v 14 Kalu abeyoęž‰ to nililoęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰ we moęž‰kudu haęž‰nalega, gioęž‰ kalu aęž‰noęž‰ sahili alitakiyoęž‰ e sendelomaęž‰ki, e oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ dowaęž‰soęž‰bo.
\v 15 \x - \xo 3.15 \xt 1Tes 5.14\x*Koęž‰sega kalu aęž‰noęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gis dowab aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ asulaęž‰soęž‰bo. Gili gaole oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowab koęž‰loęž‰, giliyoęž‰ asuloęž‰ nafale dimiaki, emoęž‰woęž‰ hagugoęž‰ towoęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰lubi.
\s1 Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ sagaloęž‰ towoęž‰ sagaęž‰foęž‰
\p 
\v 16 Alan e, haęž‰saloęž‰ dowan moęž‰woęž‰ e koęž‰loęž‰, ene haęž‰saloęž‰ dowan man aęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kelegoęž‰ tambo faęž‰laęž‰dowab aęž‰namioęž‰loęž‰, man aęž‰noęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰ dofoęž‰meleaęž‰ki soęž‰loęž‰l. Alan e gioęž‰ tambo amioęž‰ dofoęž‰melaęž‰ib.
\p 
\v 17 Ne Foęž‰l koęž‰loęž‰, sagaloęž‰ to we noęž‰noęž‰n dagileyaęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰idoęž‰. Moęž‰foęž‰s niloęž‰ tambo saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰, ninoęž‰loęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰baęž‰kiyoęž‰, niyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidaęž‰sen.
\p 
\v 18 Nili Alan, Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ ene haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰ tambo dowaęž‰biyoęž‰. 
